{"tid":1998453,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"官媒成日叫人食飯唔好分黃藍 其實係幫緊黃店","createTime":"2020-05-02T11:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:16:45.000Z","uid":149618,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"52ef518916ff6b643cf06fd5bc0a141abe3ccebf","tid":1998453,"uid":149618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/zrxhy6R.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3V7cjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3V7cjt.jpg&h=88516241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢D報紙得藍絲睇 D藍絲會信左<br />\n唔會睇黃藍就食 最後幫埋黃店<br />\n黃絲根本唔會理你照食黃店<br />\n<br />\n黃店或成最大嬴家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7777d76cddc2f96023255b3dcf36345dfab63c95","tid":1998453,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">少數霸權法則：當轉換選擇所花費既成本低時，最「堅持」既少數派係足以決定所有既人既行為模式</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n例子：點解飛機餐好少會有花生？<br />\n有嚴重花生敏感既人屬少數，大部份人其實都係食得花生<br />\n點解要因為遷就少數而犧牲大部份人喺飛機上食花生既權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為大部份人覺得飛機上唔食花生都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（唔食花生＝低成本選擇）<br />\n航空公司為免麻煩，乾脆唔提供任何花生製品<br />\n結論：少數人有花生敏感，卻迫到大部份正常人唔可以喺飛機食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間唔中一家大細或者同朋友出外食飯，同行總會有中立同藍絲，特別係廢老<br />\n對呢班唔知頭唔知路既人黎講，食咩餐廳都無所謂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">只要喺群體出外食飯時，一兩個硬頸黃絲堅持非黃絲餐廳不去（當然唔洗講出口話餐廳要係黃）<br />\n咁就可以令同行藍絲同中立都局住要食「黃金經濟圈」</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以再推想，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果每一個群體中，都有少量硬頸黃絲堅持唔幫襯藍絲企業，就足以令到社會中大部份群體都唔幫襯藍絲</strong></span><br />\n呢個就係少數硬頸撚如何取得絕對霸權既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（當然黃絲係多數派，但呢到想講既係，唔需要好多人參與，就可以改變大部份人既行為模式）<br />\n<br />\n其他例子：一大班人出街行街時，堅持唔去港鐵旗下商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好多應用例子，大家可以brainstorm一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/incerto/the-most-intolerant-wins-the-dictatorship-of-the-small-minority-3f1f83ce4e15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fincerto%2Fthe-most-intolerant-wins-the-dictatorship-of-the-small-minority-3f1f83ce4e15&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=ecfd872d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/incerto/the-most-intolerant-wins-the-dictatorship-of-the-small-minority-3f1f83ce4e15</a><br />\n<br />\nSource:［科普］少數霸權法則：迫到中立同藍絲都加入「黃金經濟圈」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1c4b3bb26320aea3b4a3bfb62a4b03a93917249","tid":1998453,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.無可疑"},{"pid":"d431b4989bd4503a97783fe1865da270c0581365","tid":1998453,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"搵紅影星做戲又係咩玩法"},{"pid":"98979d592b326e99c698c20d0ae5db830c541d21","tid":1998453,"uid":162910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqcEOTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqcEOTU.jpg&h=1864b2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/data/uCbLyMxlpGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com%2Fdata%2FuCbLyMxlpGU&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=c6007c1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com/data/uCbLyMxlpGU</a><br />\n<br />\n想呢間收皮 成日經過篤眼篤鼻<br />\n又扮連儂牆 又醫護1送1 扮撚晒野"},{"pid":"950a26c67851bec8c91b6d90dbe527761a52664d","tid":1998453,"uid":262191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"藍絲第一眼會睇圖先<br />\n佢地對呢個頭版第一印象：咩事排晒隊啊？有好野執啊<br />\n然後先睇字<br />\n最後佢地就會覺得原來班黃屍既黃色經濟圈戴係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f60fcbac2b6c6fb4bb669bc3874a01de2d82da7","tid":1998453,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:04:18.000Z","msg":"驚死無人食黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ad11125b4656f3c67b56c4229fde34dd1b6602","tid":1998453,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"你見到最旺嗰段時間間鋪冇人食就知有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e9f045888e49e6c1cd36d321573102db1f751f","tid":1998453,"uid":37524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"950a26c67851bec8c91b6d90dbe527761a52664d","tid":1998453,"uid":262191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"藍絲第一眼會睇圖先<br />\n佢地對呢個頭版第一印象：咩事排晒隊啊？有好野執啊<br />\n然後先睇字<br />\n最後佢地就會覺得原來班黃屍既黃色經濟圈戴係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"唔會有人睇佢內文啲字<br />\n太公報嘅存在只係派俾人墊煲同埋包狗屎<br />\n而且佢一向都係幫倒忙<br />\n「Once You Go Black, You Never Go Back」已經係最佳例子"}]}